  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Need more cats in your life, but you’re afraid the tons of litter sand won’t fit in your monthly budget?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fear not! Chonkers is a cozy idle game for cat lovers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open the door and welcome the most adorable stray kittens into your rooms!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/e4beb49ae3d2e52bc8218e96d876097b.poster.avif?t=1769610534\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/e4beb49ae3d2e52bc8218e96d876097b.webm?t=1769610534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/e4beb49ae3d2e52bc8218e96d876097b.mp4?t=1769610534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take a break. Relax and watch them sleep while listening to lo-fi music.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/e94d30edded734310cbe190d6af900f3.poster.avif?t=1769610534\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/e94d30edded734310cbe190d6af900f3.webm?t=1769610534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/e94d30edded734310cbe190d6af900f3.mp4?t=1769610534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with them and make them level up faster!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/14de4e43bc2fb6102b4134cbb8510cc6.poster.avif?t=1769610534\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/14de4e43bc2fb6102b4134cbb8510cc6.webm?t=1769610534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/14de4e43bc2fb6102b4134cbb8510cc6.mp4?t=1769610534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let them chonkify without worrying about health risks!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/53abcaa224cf295db13fa1e0b1e880d8.poster.avif?t=1769610534\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/53abcaa224cf295db13fa1e0b1e880d8.webm?t=1769610534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/53abcaa224cf295db13fa1e0b1e880d8.mp4?t=1769610534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>This is digital fun. Always seek professional help for your puffy little friends</i> 😸</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you’re lucky, you might also adopt the rarest galaxy wanderers. Those stray kittens from space with a mesmerizing glittery mane are in need of a new home. Give them a proper welcome ♥</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/5f92f71e2b474eec36b232dde435f1c8.poster.avif?t=1769610534\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/5f92f71e2b474eec36b232dde435f1c8.webm?t=1769610534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/5f92f71e2b474eec36b232dde435f1c8.mp4?t=1769610534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you think they’re ready for a new family, give them away for their weight in gold!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>Complete your collection book with more than 100 breeds and 400+ variants.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/0f3c5190ecb09c5d28db178102b30016.poster.avif?t=1769610534\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/0f3c5190ecb09c5d28db178102b30016.webm?t=1769610534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/0f3c5190ecb09c5d28db178102b30016.mp4?t=1769610534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If relaxation and cats are your thing, this is a game for you~<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/f072342217588ba50a10c630969a7b92.poster.avif?t=1769610534\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/f072342217588ba50a10c630969a7b92.webm?t=1769610534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/f072342217588ba50a10c630969a7b92.mp4?t=1769610534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Need more cats in your life, but you’re afraid the tons of litter sand won’t fit in your monthly budget?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fear not! Chonkers is a cozy idle game for cat lovers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open the door and welcome the most adorable stray kittens into your rooms!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/e4beb49ae3d2e52bc8218e96d876097b.poster.avif?t=1769610534\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/e4beb49ae3d2e52bc8218e96d876097b.webm?t=1769610534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/e4beb49ae3d2e52bc8218e96d876097b.mp4?t=1769610534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take a break. Relax and watch them sleep while listening to lo-fi music.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/e94d30edded734310cbe190d6af900f3.poster.avif?t=1769610534\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/e94d30edded734310cbe190d6af900f3.webm?t=1769610534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/e94d30edded734310cbe190d6af900f3.mp4?t=1769610534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with them and make them level up faster!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/